{"tid":485413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Capri座頭無保安管理費每呎4.4-4.9 如要加保安再加20%","createTime":"2017-12-01T02:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T03:52:53.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3079456f7c8d1dfa63c473285f4aae7537ebe43b","tid":485413,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"會德豐(020)將軍澳新盤Capri本月入伙，業主們興高采烈地收樓，交樓質素都未睇，一見大堂通告就扁哂咀，內容指：「如每座安排保安員當值，管理費需增加約20%」。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，一旦落實，每呎管理費將由目前4.4元至4.9元，增加至5.3元至5.9元，以最細單位實用359方呎計，每月管理費將由1,580元增至1,900元。多名業主感覺被騙，其中陳生不滿地表示，公屋都有座頭保安，現在是私樓且管理費唔平，「點解連呢啲咁基本嘅都無！」<br />\n<br />\n會德豐將軍澳新盤Capri兩年前開賣，標榜低密度臨海住宅，高座10幢呈「U」型分佈並包圍洋房，首批折實均價約1.46萬元，入場費逾400萬元。本月初陸續入伙，兩年前以近900萬元買入一伙的陳生稱：「入伙見到大堂有張通告，原來座頭居然無保安員，通告話管理費要加20%先可以有，唔係咁理想囉！公屋都有個座頭保安啦，而家係私人樓，管理費仲要唔平，講緊每呎4.5元，如果加兩成，咪5.4元，好過份！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171201/57525860\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57525860&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=962f483d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171201%2F57525860&h=cdd03b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171201/57525860</a><br />\n<br />\n好搞笑，衰過住公屋"},{"pid":"f4bb0f38e4139d1e144b3e0a4a532d7c6ae09e4a","tid":485413,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46f39a90d4579bb84c800a06db712cf84c1d8e13","tid":485413,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你豪宅黎架麻<br />\n<br />\n計果一蚊幾毫<br />\n<br />\n醜唔醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n假豪<br />\n好多連首期都要父母幫<br />\n現在每月管理費接近2k<br />\n肉疼死"},{"pid":"82f2a974609d1bbf4aaeba661754a2d26e2e8556","tid":485413,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8365a43f11b6d028b692c8cd6072a898ba43eb79","tid":485413,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"遙距保安你地識條鐵咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2538cf695b8afb99e9be190dcd950f56af62616f","tid":485413,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd34de621b6efb3de648b6394ebcdd81a6598aa4","tid":485413,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"真係公屋交一個月租都唔夠交管理費"}]}